{"talk":{"id":14392,"name":"Yasin Kakande: What's missing in the global debate over refugees","description":"In the ongoing debate over refugees, we hear from everyone -- from politicians who pledge border controls to citizens who fear they'll lose their jobs -- everyone, that is, except migrants themselves. Why are they coming? Journalist and TED Fellow Yasin Kakande explains what compelled him and many others to flee their homelands, urging a more open discussion and a new perspective. Because humanity's story, he reminds us, is a story of migration: \"There are no restrictions that could ever be so rigorous to stop the wave of migration that has determined our human history,\" he says.","slug":"yasin_kakande_what_s_missing_in_the_global_debate_over_refugees","recorded_at":"2018-04-10 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-04-16 14:54:15","updated_at":"2020-09-28 21:44:15","viewed_count":1071949,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":494,"name":"TED2018"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3a795527dcecc735b5d672ec1c536f0888d358fd_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3a795527dcecc735b5d672ec1c536f0888d358fd_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3a795527dcecc735b5d672ec1c536f0888d358fd_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3a795527dcecc735b5d672ec1c536f0888d358fd_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7237ba9d497df4cce4e706e9747770d9c17ada46_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/YasinKakande_2018U-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":2227941,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/YasinKakande_2018U-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6104891,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.t